from his Lucky Charms

303
00:13:24,303 --> 00:13:26,784
because they weren't
"Irish enough."All right.

304
00:13:26,916 --> 00:13:28,351
So you know
what I'm talking about.

305
00:13:28,481 --> 00:13:29,918
And has he ever thanked you?

306
00:13:30,048 --> 00:13:32,355
Not in so many words,

307
00:13:32,485 --> 00:13:34,879
or any words.

308
00:13:35,011 --> 00:13:37,229
Would it kill him
to actually say it?

309
00:13:38,230 --> 00:13:42,018
No. No, it wouldn't kill him.

310
00:13:43,367 --> 00:13:45,325
Leonard,

311
00:13:45,455 --> 00:13:48,372
you know how
I got the money

312
00:13:48,502 --> 00:13:51,157
to open up my
first store?

313
00:13:51,287 --> 00:13:53,202
