314
00:13:53,332 --> 00:13:56,249
'cause all the extra money
that we had had to go to Sheldon

315
00:13:56,379 --> 00:13:58,338
so he could go to
college and he could go

316
00:13:58,469 --> 00:14:00,340
study in Germany.

317
00:14:00,470 --> 00:14:03,081
And do you know
what he's never said to me?

318
00:14:03,213 --> 00:14:05,955
Danke schon?

319
00:14:06,825 --> 00:14:09,393
It's... "thank you" in German.

320
00:14:09,523 --> 00:14:12,221
Do you need me
to sit on your head?

321
00:14:12,351 --> 00:14:14,790
Nope.

322
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:16,878
After all my sacrifices,

323
00:14:17,008 --> 00:14:19,925
guess which kid
my mom is the most proud of.

324
00:14:21,970 --> 00:14:23,928
If it makes you feel any better,

325
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:26,975
my mom's most proud
of Sheldon, too, so...

326
00:14:27,889 --> 00:14:29,065
Leonard,

327
00:14:29,195 --> 00:14:30,543
you want a beer?

328
00:14:30,675 --> 00:14:32,503
I would love a beer.

329
00:14:32,633 --> 00:14:34,330
There you go.

330
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:36,768
Thanks. Can you open it for me?No, it's a twist-off.

331
