I know.

332
00:14:47,604 --> 00:14:49,562
Hey!

333
00:14:49,694 --> 00:14:52,783
I got all the beads
to the other side.

334
00:14:54,176 --> 00:14:56,221
It's not a puzzle, Penny.

335
00:14:56,353 --> 00:14:59,095
Do you really want
to be touching that?

336
00:14:59,225 --> 00:15:01,096
Do you know how
many sick kids...?

337
00:15:01,226 --> 00:15:03,926
You know, never mind.
Knock yourself out.

338
00:15:06,493 --> 00:15:08,017
Bernadette says
they're checking the kids now.

339
00:15:08,147 --> 00:15:10,105
You know, maybe
we didn't allneed to come.

340
00:15:10,235 --> 00:15:13,152
Hey, whatever kind of pink eye
their kids have, I have,

341
00:15:13,282 --> 00:15:14,763
and I need to know.

342
00:15:14,893 --> 00:15:17,200
And if it's viral, I'm screwed.

343
00:15:17,330 --> 00:15:20,377
Maybe not. You know, I know it's
not traditional wedding attire,

344
00:15:20,507 --> 00:15:23,032
but how about
a welder's mask?

345
00:15:23,162 --> 00:15:24,119
If you know

346
00:15:25,512 --> 00:15:26,470
a welder, that could be
your "something borrowed."

347
00:15:29,298 --> 00:15:31,127
