00:15:32,431 --> 00:15:33,782
Yes.

350
00:15:33,912 --> 00:15:35,261
What are you doing?
Wash your hands!

351
00:15:35,392 --> 00:15:37,263
Not you.

352
00:15:40,353 --> 00:15:42,225
Hello. Room service?

353
00:15:42,354 --> 00:15:45,489
I'm calling about
the club sandwich on your menu.

354
00:15:45,619 --> 00:15:48,056
No, I-I don't want one.

355
00:15:48,186 --> 00:15:50,146
I just want you
to spell it correctly.

356
00:15:51,887 --> 00:15:54,802
Unless the "club"
is the Poor Typing Club.

357
00:15:54,932 --> 00:15:56,369
Okay.

358
00:15:56,499 --> 00:16:01,810
Now let's discuss
this 15% "gratooty"?

359
00:16:03,027 --> 00:16:05,988
Well, that was rude.

