Yes.

363
00:16:15,475 --> 00:16:17,651
Like that, but nicer,
and that way.

364
00:16:17,782 --> 00:16:20,566
I have nothing
to apologize for.

365
00:16:20,697 --> 00:16:22,569
I told you this was a bad idea.

366
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:24,397
Sometimes you
can't patch a tire.

367
00:16:24,527 --> 00:16:26,355
You just got to
buy a new one.

368
00:16:26,485 --> 00:16:28,009
Actually, that's
always the case.

369
00:16:28,139 --> 00:16:30,576
Never patch, buy new.

370
00:16:30,707 --> 00:16:34,015
While I appreciate
your folksy tire wisdom,

371
00:16:34,146 --> 00:16:36,627
