Shut up!

376
00:16:42,633 --> 00:16:45,330
You went away to
college after Dad died.

377
00:16:45,461 --> 00:16:47,071
Who do you think took
care of everything?

378
00:16:47,202 --> 00:16:50,902
Mom did. Mom always
took care of everything.

379
00:16:51,032 --> 00:16:53,383
Mom was a mess, Missy
was a dumb teenager.

380
00:16:53,513 --> 00:16:55,514
I had to look
after both of 'em.

381
00:16:55,646 --> 00:16:57,213
I talked to Mom
all the time.

382
00:16:57,343 --> 00:16:59,258
If she was upset,
she would have told me.

383
00:16:59,388 --> 00:17:01,956
She was protecting
you, you idiot,

384
00:17:02,086 --> 00:17:03,566
just like everyone
always does.

385
00:17:03,696 --> 00:17:05,569
If things were bad,

386
00:17:05,698 --> 00:17:06,570
