387
00:17:07,876 --> 00:17:09,225
Because Iwas
protecting you, too.

388
00:17:12,401 --> 00:17:14,230
You're my baby brother, Sheldon.

389
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:17,146
I know life has been
hard for you,

390
00:17:17,275 --> 00:17:21,019
